structure.unit: A UNIFORM MILITARY AND OVERSEAS VOTERS ACT

law.catch_line: Chapter may modify or supersede federal act.
law.text: To the extent permitted by Section 102 of the Electronic Signatures in Global and National Commerce Act, Pub. L. No. 106-229, 15 U.S.C. sec. 7002, this chapter may modify or supersede provisions of that act.
law.history: Created 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 131, sec. 20, effective July 1, 2014.
